performance_details.query: q = load "lead4"; q = filter q by {{cell(time_dropdown.selection, 0, "current").asDateRange("date('CreatedDate_Year', 'CreatedDate_Month', 'CreatedDate_Day')")}}; q = group q by 'Id'; q = foreach q generate first('Name') as 'Name', first('Company') as 'Company', first('State') as 'State', first('Industry') as 'Industry', first('UserOrQueueName') as 'UserOrQueueName', first('Rating') as 'Rating', first('LeadSource') as 'LeadSource', first('IsConverted') as 'IsConverted', first('ConvertedDate') as 'ConvertedDate', sum('LeadAge') as 'sum_LeadAge';

conversion_rate.query: leads = load "lead4"; leads = filter leads by {{cell(time_dropdown.selection, 0, "current").asDateRange("date('CreatedDate_Year', 'CreatedDate_Month', 'CreatedDate_Day')")}}; converted = filter leads by 'IsConverted' == "true"; converted = group converted by all; converted = foreach converted generate count() as 'count_converted'; leads = group leads by all; leads = foreach leads generate count() as 'count_all'; q = group leads by all full, converted by all; q = foreach q generate sum(leads['count_all']) as 'count_all', sum(converted['count_converted']) as 'count_converted'; q = foreach q generate coalesce('count_converted' / 'count_all', 0) as 'sum_percent';
